title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table inside a grid cell
description: Description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data from tables inside a grid cell, the data should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Export data from tables inside the grid cell.
Expected result: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
Actual result: Exception is thrown at ReportEngineService.getMetaData().
